name: Easey Street murders
summary: A significant breakthrough has been made in a decades-old cold case, as a suspect in the 1977 "Easey Street murders" in Melbourne has been apprehended in Italy. The arrest of this Greek Australian dual national, almost 50 years after the brutal murders of two women, has been hailed as a major development in one of Melbourne's oldest unsolved cases. The suspect, whose name has been released as Evangelos Goussis, is believed to have been involved in the gruesome double homicide. The arrest, made in Rome, marks a significant turn in the investigation into a case that has haunted the Collingwood community for decades.

name: Greg Malouf
summary: Renowned Australian celebrity chef Greg Malouf, known as the "Godfather of Middle Eastern Cuisine," has passed away at the age of 64 in Dubai. Malouf gained fame for his Lebanese culinary expertise and was recognized for his significant contributions to the culinary world. His death has sparked an outpouring of tributes from the culinary community in both Australia and the Middle East, with co-stars and fellow chefs expressing their grief and acknowledging his legacy as a culinary giant.

name: Oscar McInerney
summary: Brisbane Lions ruckman Oscar McInerney will regrettably miss the 2024 AFL Grand Final after suffering a double shoulder dislocation during the Lions' preliminary final victory over Geelong. The injury occurred during a fierce contest in the first half, resulting in McInerney receiving extensive treatment on the field. Brisbane coach Chris Fagan confirmed the heartbreaking news, expressing disappointment over the loss of their key player. McInerney's absence leaves a significant void in the Lions' lineup, as he has been a vital contributor throughout the season. Despite the setback, Brisbane emerged victorious in the preliminary final, setting up a thrilling grand final showdown against the winner of the Collingwood and Sydney semi-final.

name: His Three Daughters
summary: Netflix's "His Three Daughters" has garnered critical acclaim as an exceptional drama. Starring Elizabeth Olsen, Natasha Lyonne, and Carrie Coon, the film explores the complexities of family dynamics as three sisters navigate the impending death of their father. Set in a small New York apartment, the film's intimate setting intensifies the tensions and sibling clashes, showcasing the actresses' powerful performances. Critics have praised the exquisite judgment in the film's direction, highlighting its ability to both tear a family apart and bring them back together. The emotional depth and powerhouse cast have resonated with audiences, leading to rave reviews. "His Three Daughters" has been hailed as one of the best dramas of the year, cementing its place as a must-watch for fans of compelling family dramas.

name: Colin Farrell
summary: Colin Farrell's portrayal of the Penguin in the HBO series has garnered critical acclaim. His powerful performance, despite the cumbersome prosthetics, has earned praise for its authenticity and emotional depth. The show's success has been attributed to Farrell's charismatic portrayal, which has captivated audiences with a blend of menace and vulnerability. Farrell's appearance at the Emmys, where he walked out to the "60s Batman Theme," further cemented his status as an outstanding actor. Notable outlets such as Forbes, GQ, and USA TODAY have lauded his performance, with The Guardian declaring that he deserves awards recognition for his exceptional portrayal. Farrell's transformation into the character has also impressed his co-stars, demonstrating the level of commitment and dedication he brought to the role.

name: MotoGP
summary: The MotoGP World Championship returns to Misano for a replacement round, and the 2024 MotoGP Emilia Romagna Grand Prix will take place there. Marc Marquez leads the "Misano 2" MotoGP weekend, while Francesco Bagnaia leads the second practice session of the MotoGP Emilia Romagna GP. The Emilia-Romagna Grand Prix qualifying session has begun, and the 2025 MotoGP rider lineup has been confirmed. Liberty Media's €4bn MotoGP takeover is facing scrutiny from an F1 rival, and Bagnaia has narrowed Martin's MotoGP lead with a sprint win at Emilia-Romagna. The 2025 MotoGP season will feature a calendar and rider lineup, while Yamaha is implementing a significant change in its MotoGP engine philosophy.
